Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在正被逼至绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，他却在享受这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.42,0:00:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打从内心，兴奋的期待着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9局下半，两出局满垒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙现在脑里只想着\N要把球打出场外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Venom(猛毒)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙现在正朝着球场走去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊爆危机\N FULL METAL PANlC
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#24 lNTO THE BLUE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.75,0:01:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真高兴啊，卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九龙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C3系统第11号电源线被切断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从C4转接过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电力丧失20%
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机库C区探测到火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2气密门的内壁破损
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内温度上升
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机库防火隔间无法关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手动关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁在那附近？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7、8、9蓄水池破损
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会失去平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注40的水进第10至15蓄水池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急排出所有的喷射燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷第2、第3 ECS杆损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来把那个粗暴的家伙\N给我赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没辄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你赢了，卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，好像也不是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动SDM，120秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告，启动后无法解除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您同意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，快点动手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你会陪我到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算自我引爆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们来当好朋友吧，卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舱门？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，还剩60秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附带一提，炸药有300公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,份量足以炸沉这艘船舰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，你要怎么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射主动鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射主动鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巴萨狄那的主动鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从方位2-9-8接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好诱饵机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快准备再度潜行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高压空气尚未充填完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离2500
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认鱼雷发射管口的开启声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.27,0:07:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说想跟你说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈啰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁…阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，长官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除所有攻击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻返回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就等于是终于得到了\N期望已久的初次打击机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛却因太阳西下而告中止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼雷没来？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跟丢了我方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴萨狄那，在距离1500处停止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有发射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行舱门正在开启
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种暴风雨中\N打开飞行舱门根本是自杀行为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Danann没有任何异常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令是从别处发出的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(不用担心，一切都会很顺利)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事的，不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？这副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很难看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你像英雄那般\N帅气的将我一次击倒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死命挣扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起华丽又滑稽的走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗，卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩30秒
