Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射，千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认全舰的空气密闭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以关闭飞行舱门为优先
