Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不危险吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里，千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是钓竿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说那个，这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密的钓场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地里只有我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钓鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要搭往东京的班机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能在这里\N再待40多分钟而已耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:19:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我当初的作战目标
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:19:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本就是想带你来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果却因为各种事而绕了一大圈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…到这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来，钓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定30分钟就可以钓到大鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就很难说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得什么都做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是钓上超乎想像的大鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是从恐怖的危险中逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30分钟就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微陪我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的这么觉得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有你在，我现在才能在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就来试试\N你所说的这种好运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拉了，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:20:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鲷鱼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.06,0:21:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是鲸鱼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不能否定这个可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要把它钓回家去喔，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
